; Zilbershtein loan reconstruction
; Tamar and Z co-invested in Betegy sp. z o.o. via Prodigy Investments Ltd (Malta).
; All cash came from Tamar. Half of all payments into Betegy/Prodigy and related fees
; are economically loans to Z. No formal loan agreement.
; Prodigy later dissolved; Betegy shares distributed 50/50 to Z and Tamar.
;
; Principal: EUR 334,560.94 (approximate - PLN amounts converted at Frankfurter mid-rates)
;   - Half of PLN investments: EUR 310,321.08
;   - Half of professional fees: EUR 24,239.86
; Interest: EUR 22,593.06
; Total repaid: EUR 357,154.00 (5 payments, Nov 2020)
; Outstanding: zero
;
; EUR amounts may be revised if actual bank FX conversion records surface.

